flowchart LR
  a([All month<br/>the team's work flows into Relay<br/>tasks · worklogs · meetings · KPIs]):::start

  b[25th of the month<br/>AI reviews the month<br/>planned vs delivered · gaps · risks]:::model

  c[Draft roadmap ready<br/>+ pointed questions<br/>for the team lead]:::proc

  d[Lead reviews in chat<br/>one question at a time<br/>click an option or type]:::proc

  e[One click to finalize]:::proc

  f[(Next month's goals<br/>live in Relay)]:::store

  g([Every answer teaches the AI<br/>next month's draft starts sharper]):::start

  a --> b --> c --> d --> e --> f --> g
  g -. the loop repeats every month .-> a

